{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344190/extras/monster_4_1.gif?t=1734104525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Get ready to put your mouse to use and get smack talked by a bunch of pixels!\u00a0 <br><strong><i>Orpheus' Revenge</i>\u00a0is an 80s inspired arcade shooter with more sass than sense. Pixel graphics, neon colours and electronic beats meet greek mythology.</strong>  <br> <br>You\u2019re Orpheus, back in the underworld, armed only with your reflexes and precious little health as you fight through Hades' ranks of undead and even hell's generals. They\u2019ll taunt you, they\u2019ll insult your aim, and if you\u2019re really unlucky, they might actually hit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344190/extras/section.png?t=1734104525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pixel Art &amp; Neon</strong>: Orpheus' Revenge is an 80s style arcade game. Enjoy vibrant scenes and synth wave beats!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Click-to-Kill Mayhem</strong>: Shoot monsters by clicking as fast as you can. No waiting times, no second client. Start the game and click away.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Trash-Talking Bosses</strong>: Why face internet strangers, when you can have a bunch of pixels insult you?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>High Score:</strong>\u00a0How high can you fly? Record your best 10 attempts and get good!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3344190/extras/monster_6_1.gif?t=1734104525\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Level 1","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/pu